{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"887d041e-8403-4180-9d50-13d749dc415c","content":"**No, `net6.0` is not supported by MSTest v4.** MSTest 4.x dropped support for .NET 6 (and all out-of-support TFMs). The minimum supported frameworks are:\n\n- **net8.0** (or newer)\n- **net462** (for .NET Framework)\n\n.NET 6 reached end-of-life in November 2024, so MSTest v4 removed it.\n\nYou'll need to update your `TargetFramework` to at least `net8.0` before upgrading. Want me to make both changes (TFM + MSTest v4)?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"e8cd4851-b469-44d3-aee0-59c083d84ecc","outputTokens":148,"requestId":"3407:14762F:1001903:12BCC02:69F41511"},"id":"e74f2a43-d199-4053-b799-22a66f20342a","timestamp":"2026-05-01T02:51:03.023Z","parentId":"ea0b936d-21fe-4f76-a028-b11d5008c733"}
